---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | Tajinder Singh" description="About Tajinder Singh, Solutions Architect focused on automation and edge/data systems.">
	<Container size="wide">
		<section class="section">
			<SectionHeading
				eyebrow="About"
				title="Architecture That Reduces Operational Drag"
				description="I work at the intersection of edge infrastructure, automation, and data systems."
			/>
			<div class="about-copy">
				<p>
					I am Tajinder Singh (Taj), a solutions architect focused on shipping systems that are reliable in
					production, not just good in diagrams. Most of my work centers on automation-heavy products that need
					a strong edge entry layer, clean event flows, and practical observability.
				</p>
				<p>
					Across client and platform work, I design Cloudflare Worker routing, verification pipelines, and
					workflow orchestration patterns using n8n and API-driven services. I prioritize architecture that teams
					can maintain without constant firefighting.
				</p>
				<p>
					My approach is straightforward: clarify constraints, design for failure modes early, and optimize for
					operational leverage so teams ship faster with fewer regressions.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section split">
			<article class="card">
				<h2>What I Focus On</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Edge verification and request governance with Cloudflare Workers + Turnstile.</li>
					<li>Automation architecture using n8n for event-driven operations and integrations.</li>
					<li>Search/data systems with ingestion pipelines and stable schema contracts.</li>
					<li>Pragmatic API orchestration across Xano and custom service layers.</li>
				</ul>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h2>Highlights</h2>
				<ol class="timeline">
					<li>
						<strong>2026</strong>
						<p>Launched verification-first intake architecture linking Webflow, Turnstile, Workers, and n8n.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>2025</strong>
						<p>Built a Meilisearch ingestion platform with staged indexing and faceted query governance.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>2025</strong>
						<p>Implemented smart edge cache policies and hotlink protection for high-traffic asset delivery.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Ongoing</strong>
						<p>Advising teams on automation migrations and event architecture for operational scalability.</p>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</article>
		</section>
	</Container>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	.section {
		margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
	}

	.about-copy {
		max-width: 56rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.8rem;
	}

	.split {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.card {
		padding: 1.2rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg-elevated) 90%, transparent);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	.card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.15rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.65rem;
	}

	.timeline {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.95rem;
	}

	.timeline li {
		padding-left: 0.85rem;
		border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.timeline p {
		margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.split {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
